---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - IVS Legal" description="IVS Legal's privacy policy. Learn how we protect and process your personal data." lang="en">
  <Header />
  
  <main>
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-navy-900 to-navy-800 text-white py-20">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
          <h1 class="text-5xl font-serif font-bold mb-6">
            Privacy <span class="text-gold-400">Policy</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
            Your privacy is fundamental to us. Learn how we protect 
            and process your personal data.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Content -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-white">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto prose prose-lg">
          <div class="bg-gold-50 p-6 rounded-lg mb-8">
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2"><strong>Last updated:</strong> January 1, 2024</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
              This Privacy Policy complies with the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) 
              and applicable Portuguese legislation.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-8">
            <section>
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-navy-900 mb-4">1. Data Controller Identification</h2>
              <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
                <p><strong>Company Name:</strong> IVS Legal - Law Firm</p>
                <p><strong>Address:</strong> Travessa Henrique Schreck 96, 4450-578 Matosinhos, Portugal</p>
                <p><strong>Email:</strong> geral@ivs.legal</p>
                <p><strong>Phone:</strong> +351 925 395 905</p>
                <!-- <p><strong>Tax ID:</strong> 123456789</p> -->
              </div>
            </section>

            <section>
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-navy-900 mb-4">2. Personal Data Collected</h2>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
                We collect and process the following types of personal data:
              </p>
              <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-700">
                <li><strong>Identification data:</strong> Name, surname, date of birth, identification number</li>
                <li><strong>Contact data:</strong> Postal address, email, phone number</li>
                <li><strong>Professional data:</strong> Profession, company, position</li>
                <li><strong>Navigation data:</strong> IP address, cookies, website usage data</li>
                <li><strong>Legal case data:</strong> Information necessary for providing legal services</li>
              </ul>
            </section>

            <section>
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-navy-900 mb-4">3. Processing Purposes</h2>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
                Your personal data is processed for the following purposes:
              </p>
              <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
                  <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy-900 mb-2">Service Provision</h3>
                  <ul class="text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-1">
                    <li>• Legal consultancy</li>
                    <li>• Legal representation</li>
                    <li>• Document preparation</li>
                    <li>• Case monitoring</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
                  <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy-900 mb-2">Communication</h3>
                  <ul class="text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-1">
                    <li>• Response to information requests</li>
                    <li>• Consultation scheduling</li>
                    <li>• Newsletter sending</li>
                    <li>• Promotional communications</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
                  <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy-900 mb-2">Legal Obligations</h3>
                  <ul class="text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-1">
                    <li>• Compliance with tax obligations</li>
                    <li>• Document archiving</li>
                    <li>• Money laundering prevention</li>
                    <li>• Cooperation with authorities</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
                  <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy-900 mb-2">Service Improvement</h3>
                  <ul class="text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-1">
                    <li>• Satisfaction analysis</li>
                    <li>• Website optimization</li>
                    <li>• New service development</li>
                    <li>• Statistical studies</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>
            </section>

            <section>
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-navy-900 mb-4">4. Legal Basis for Processing</h2>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
                The processing of your personal data is based on the following legal bases:
              </p>
              <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-700">
                <li><strong>Consent:</strong> For promotional communications and newsletters</li>
                <li><strong>Contract performance:</strong> For providing legal services</li>
                <li><strong>Legal obligation:</strong> For compliance with legal and regulatory duties</li>
                <li><strong>Legitimate interest:</strong> For service improvement and security</li>
              </ul>
            </section>

            <section>
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-navy-900 mb-4">5. Data Sharing</h2>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
                Your personal data may be shared with:
              </p>
              <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-700">
                <li><strong>Collaborators and partners:</strong> Lawyers, solicitors, experts</li>
                <li><strong>Service providers:</strong> Accountants, IT companies, postal services</li>
                <li><strong>Competent authorities:</strong> Courts, Bar Association, tax authorities</li>
                <li><strong>Authorized third parties:</strong> Only with your express consent</li>
              </ul>
            </section>

            <section>
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-navy-900 mb-4">6. Retention Period</h2>
              <div class="bg-gold-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
                <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
                  Personal data is retained for the following periods:
                </p>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-700">
                  <li><strong>Client data:</strong> 20 years after the end of the relationship (Bar Association Statute)</li>
                  <li><strong>Contact data:</strong> Until consent revocation</li>
                  <li><strong>Navigation data:</strong> 13 months (cookies)</li>
                  <li><strong>Tax data:</strong> 10 years (VAT Code)</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </section>

            <section>
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-navy-900 mb-4">7. Your Rights</h2>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
                Under the GDPR, you have the following rights:
              </p>
              <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                <div class="border border-gold-200 p-4 rounded-lg">
                  <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy-900 mb-2">Right of Access</h3>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">Obtain information about the data we process</p>
                </div>
                <div class="border border-gold-200 p-4 rounded-lg">
                  <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy-900 mb-2">Right of Rectification</h3>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">Correct inaccurate or incomplete data</p>
                </div>
                <div class="border border-gold-200 p-4 rounded-lg">
                  <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy-900 mb-2">Right to Erasure</h3>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">Request deletion of your data</p>
                </div>
                <div class="border border-gold-200 p-4 rounded-lg">
                  <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy-900 mb-2">Right to Restriction</h3>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">Restrict data processing</p>
                </div>
                <div class="border border-gold-200 p-4 rounded-lg">
                  <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy-900 mb-2">Right to Portability</h3>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">Receive data in structured format</p>
                </div>
                <div class="border border-gold-200 p-4 rounded-lg">
                  <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy-900 mb-2">Right to Object</h3>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">Object to data processing</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </section>

            <section>
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-navy-900 mb-4">8. Data Security</h2>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
                We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your data:
              </p>
              <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-700">
                <li>Encryption of sensitive data</li>
                <li>Restricted access control</li>
                <li>Regular and secure backup</li>
                <li>Regular staff training</li>
                <li>Periodic security audits</li>
              </ul>
            </section>

            <section>
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-navy-900 mb-4">9. Cookies</h2>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
                Our website uses cookies to improve the browsing experience. 
                You can manage your preferences through your browser settings.
              </p>
              <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy-900 mb-2">Types of Cookies:</h3>
                <ul class="text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-1">
                  <li>• <strong>Essential:</strong> Necessary for website functionality</li>
                  <li>• <strong>Functional:</strong> Improve functionality and personalization</li>
                  <li>• <strong>Analytical:</strong> Help us understand how you use the website</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </section>

            <section>
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-navy-900 mb-4">10. Contact and Exercise of Rights</h2>
              <div class="bg-navy-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
                <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
                  To exercise your rights or clarify doubts about this policy, contact us:
                </p>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                  <div>
                    <p><strong>Email:</strong> geral@ivs.legal</p>
                    <p><strong>Phone:</strong> +351 925 395 905</p>
                    <p><strong>Mail:</strong> Travessa Henrique Schreck 96, 4450-578 Matosinhos</p>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
                      <strong>Supervisory Authority:</strong><br>
                      National Data Protection Commission (CNPD)<br>
                      Website: www.cnpd.pt
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </section>

            <section>
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-navy-900 mb-4">11. Policy Changes</h2>
              <p class="text-gray-700">
                This Privacy Policy may be updated periodically. 
                Changes will be communicated through our website and, when applicable, 
                by email. We recommend regularly checking this page to stay informed.
              </p>
            </section>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .prose h2 {
    @apply border-b border-gold-200 pb-2;
  }
  
  .prose ul {
    @apply text-gray-700;
  }
  
  .prose strong {
    @apply text-navy-900;
  }
</style>